desc: Keep your favourite beer nitro coffee fresh and carbonated down to the last drop with this amazing KEGWERKS GROWLER KEG. Made of durable, high grade stainless steel — the same material used in commercial beer kegs — the indestructible beer keg is single-wall insulated and has a no-leak cap that seals in CO2

layout.text: Fill your GROWLER at your favourite Microbrewery - Enjoy Fresh Craft Beer at Home
